Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.14,0:44:48.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能不要再告诉别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to keep this information to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.56,0:44:50.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,这事挺闹心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.02,0:44:52.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,也不只是闹心了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.39,0:44:55.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些就交给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.18,0:44:57.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我可能还会找你帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I may need your help again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.02,0:45:02.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可是又给我添了不少要办的事情啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've certainly given me a lot to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.61,0:45:08.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,办事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.38,0:45:29.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,道吉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dougie?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.99,0:45:33.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,你真是...  挺有趣的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're an-- an interesting fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.55,0:46:02.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是琼斯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You Jones?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.02,0:46:03.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我  我们就直说了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes. Now let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.95,0:46:05.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,给我解释一下道吉到底干了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Explain to me exactly what Dougie did
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.49,0:46:07.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,才欠了你们的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to make him owe you money.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.17,0:46:08.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,他借的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He borrowed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.97,0:46:10.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫"他借的"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you mean, "He borrowed it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.57,0:46:12.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,他赌了一场橄榄球赛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He took points on a football game.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.77,0:46:14.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,后来胃口大了  加了双倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He got greedy, he doubled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.62,0:46:16.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,结果最后没赢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It didn't work out for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.22,0:46:18.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,赔了两万  还有利息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Out 20 grand he was, plus interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.25,0:46:20.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,这已经是三周前的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, that was three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.20,0:46:22.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,利息还在加呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Meter's still running.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.07,0:46:23.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经涨到五万二了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's up to 52.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.75,0:46:26.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,先让我来捋一捋  有这么一场球赛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So let me get this straight. People were playing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.03,0:46:28.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,他打了个赌输了两万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He made a bet where he lost $20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.30,0:46:31.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后你们想让他给五万二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you want him to pay you back $52,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.90,0:46:33.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very good. That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.53,0:46:35.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那你们听清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, so you get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.15,0:46:37.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的丈夫有份工作  结了婚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My husband has a job; he has a wife;
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.16,0:46:39.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有个孩子  他挣的钱根本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he has a child; he does not make enough money
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.15,0:46:42.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,拿不出五万二  不管是干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to pay back $52,000 for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.80,0:46:44.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们算不上有钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are not wealthy people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.14,0:46:45.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,开的都是廉价的破车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We drive cheap, terrible cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.86,0:46:47.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是些平民百姓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are the 99 percenters.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.45,0:46:48.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经被欺负的够多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we are shit on enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.70,0:46:50.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们绝对忍不了再听任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we are certainly not gonna be shit on
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.22,0:46:51.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们这种人摆布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}by the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.38,0:46:52.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过  女士...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nevertheless, lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.83,0:46:54.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们就这么办了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So here's what we're gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.93,0:46:56.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我不知情的情况下  我丈夫找你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Without my knowledge, my husband came to you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.68,0:46:58.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,借了两万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for a loan of $20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.34,0:46:59.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们也很好心的借给他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were nice enough to give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.86,0:47:01.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,但他决不该像这个样子赌钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But he should never have been gambling like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.92,0:47:03.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会把钱还给你们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna pay you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.17,0:47:04.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过在银行里  我们就只挣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, at my bank, where we make
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.53,0:47:06.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,不到百分之一的利息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}less than one percent interest
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.06,0:47:07.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,原本存的钱也不多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}on what little money we have,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.78,0:47:09.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,你借钱能要到百分之二十五的利息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}people would be turning cartwheels
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.32,0:47:11.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,就该高兴到翻跟头了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just to get 25 percent interest on any loan,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.72,0:47:13.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些就是我现在很大方的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and that is what I'm generously
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.10,0:47:14.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备给你们的数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}gonna give to you right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.34,0:47:17.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,两万五千块\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}$25,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.15,0:47:19.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些就是我第一次  也是最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is my first, last,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.22,0:47:22.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,会给你们的全部的钱  仅此一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and only offer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.90,0:47:26.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,这究竟是个什么世道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What kind of world are we living in
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.53,0:47:27.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,才会有你们这种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where people can behave like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.93,0:47:29.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,竟能这个样子对别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Treat other people this way
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.04,0:47:30.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,毫无恻隐之情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}without any compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.44,0:47:32.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,也不体谅他人的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or feeling for their suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.82,0:47:34.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们生存在一个无比黑暗的年代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are living in a dark, dark age,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.00,0:47:36.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,而你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.67,0:47:38.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,也是问题根源的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}are part of the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.66,0:47:41.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我建议你们好好看看你们自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, I suggest you take a good, long look at yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.35,0:47:44.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我再也不想看到你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because I never want to see either of you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.82,0:48:00.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,这小妞真狠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tough dame.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.51,0:48:02.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,真狠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.62,0:48:07.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫他不在车里  三具尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you mean he wasn't in the car? Three bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.92,0:49:05.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.06,0:49:39.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.52,0:51:05.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}奈兹·珀斯制造
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.69,0:52:08.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.40,0:52:10.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,上女厕所  查德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Use the ladies' room, Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.15,0:52:12.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.87,0:52:13.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  查德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, Chad,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.95,0:52:15.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,去别的隔间上厕所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}use another restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.73,0:52:20.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,你和警长说过了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clear this with the sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.09,0:52:26.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不说的话我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll tell him if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.22,0:52:30.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,去说吧  查德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, you do that, Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.35,0:53:05.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,写报告一点都没意思  伙计们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Filling out paperwork's no fun, fellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.54,0:53:08.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  但是总得写\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know that, but, uh, gotta be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.74,0:53:11.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,等你做完...这堆破事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when you finish... That motherfucking piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.35,0:53:12.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要你处理...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...I want you to handle that...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.92,0:53:16.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,惊喜吧  惊喜吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, surprise, surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.45,0:53:19.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有修好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.00,0:53:20.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  多丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's that, Doris?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.09,0:53:21.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸的车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dad's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.63,0:53:23.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上他要开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This morning he went to drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.12,0:53:25.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,根本开不出车道  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}couldn't even get it out of the driveway, Frank!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.51,0:53:27.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,只会一晃一晃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It just lurched and lurched.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.66,0:53:30.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,他应该没有放手刹吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sounds like he left the emergency brake on.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.79,0:53:33.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我爸爸不知道怎么开车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you telling me my father doesn't know how to drive a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.36,0:53:34.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是想说这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that what you're telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.47,0:53:35.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你别想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't you dare,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.92,0:53:38.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,你别想把这开不了的破车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}don't you dare try to blame my father
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.30,0:53:39.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,怪到我爸爸头上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for that car not running right!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.97,0:53:41.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果能让你好受点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll get it looked at again
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.55,0:53:42.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就再找人来看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if it'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.48,0:53:44.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,好受点  好受点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Feel better? Feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.23,0:53:49.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  你为什么老和我对着干  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why, why are you always against me, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.24,0:53:50.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,去我办公室吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go to my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.88,0:53:53.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们修得太差了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They did a lousy job fixing that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.74,0:53:55.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们得修好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They have to make it right,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.30,0:53:57.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,不然我们就不付钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or we're not paying them until they do!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.35,0:54:00.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,换我可不会受她这种鸟气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I sure wouldn't take that kind of shit off her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.88,0:54:04.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.12,0:54:07.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道你自己在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.79,0:54:10.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, yeah? How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.06,0:54:13.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,算了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.59,0:54:14.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.90,0:54:16.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是个自由的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.06,0:54:18.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能表达我的观点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can voice my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.77,0:54:20.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你当然可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, you sure can.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.07,0:54:22.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥们儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.38,0:54:24.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,她以前不是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She didn't use to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.66,0:54:27.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道他们儿子自杀了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't know that their son committed suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.13,0:54:29.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我听说过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I heard something about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.91,0:54:33.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,他受不了成为士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He couldn't take being a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.76,0:54:46.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,警局  有什么紧急情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sheriff's Department. What's your emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.98,0:54:49.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where's your location?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.70,0:54:54.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,你电话多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's your telephone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.03,0:55:11.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,*跪到地上*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*Hit the ground*
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.82,0:55:13.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,*院子里*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*The yard*
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.09,0:55:16.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,*我发现了什么*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}*I found something*
